---
/* The site is dark-only. This override drops Starlight's system-preference
   detection so a light-mode OS can't pull the page into a half-broken light
   theme. data-theme is pinned to dark before the first paint. */
---

{/* Inlined so the theme is set before paint, which avoids a flash. */}
<script is:inline>
	document.documentElement.dataset.theme = 'dark';
</script>
